  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is filed under the Minimal conformance profile; a sha256 content hash is present for traceability, but the ed25519 digital signature has not yet been applied — the signature workflow is pending sponsor approval. All 13 credibility factors are assessed. Package integrity cannot be cryptographically verified until the signature field is populated.",
