      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented V&V test suite, version control, and regression testing consistent with MRL 5 requirements (Gradation 4).",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver has version control and basic regression tests but lacks a formally documented V&V test suite traceable to FDA guidance. Achieved level 2 against required level 4; gap remains open."
    },
    {
