      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and manufactured solution benchmarks must confirm solver correctness for turbulent rotating-frame flows at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Only Taylor-Green vortex benchmarks were performed; manufactured solution verification for rotating-frame hemolysis transport equations was not completed. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
